text: Aerenea panamensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2010. It is known from Panama.BioLib.cz - Aerenea panamensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 2010
